text = "v0.6 Regional Weather Boundary\n\nAuthoritative Controller\n- six data-driven weather definitions\n- public 30-60 second forecast lead\n- one region per event, at most two events\n- 45-90 second active phase plus 10 second fade\n- economy / route / monster / military / intel effects\n- card-authored events and v2 save data\n\nmain.gd legacy engine remains deleted; no parallel owner."
